{"tid":52442,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[實戰] 月供美股SPY - 12月","createTime":"2016-12-24T05:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T08:36:01.000Z","uid":34976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba18e8320244c7cdea052222b2b0c342dfca6ad","tid":52442,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"月供即是強迫自己每個月投入一定資金投資，亦即利用平均成本法投資<br />\n我沒有研究過其他投資策略，對風險承受能力亦稍低(心理因素)，因此我會選擇以平均成本法買入指數型ETF<br />\n<br />\n以下是由2016年12月開始的月供SPY記錄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4T9Xg5W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4T9Xg5W.jpg&h=6d74722f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U9250U3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU9250U3.jpg&h=8ca16bb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(所使用APPS為JStock)<br />\n<br />\n常見問題<br />\nQ1. 何謂平均成本法?<br />\nA1. 關於平均成本法之好壞處可參考拙文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/28980/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flihkg.na.cx%2Fthread%2F28980%2Fpage%2F1&d=L8MSUQG7MI8HI5HnTx9053vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=81d01a2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/28980/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nQ2. 為什麼選美股?<br />\nA2. 有很多不同原因<br />\n一、美股沒有碎股，可以逐股買賣，對資金較少的投資者有利<br />\n二、承上，由於可小額買入股票，每月買入股票的時間、投資額更有彈性<br />\n三、美市比港市有更穩定的增長，HSI在近5年波幅橫行時，美國三大指數升幅接近一倍<br />\n四、港股愈來愈受中資影響<br />\n五、直接持有美元資產<br />\n<br />\nQ3. 什麼是SPY?<br />\nA3. 美股與港股不同，不是以數字編號而是以簡寫作代號(如Facebook股票代號為&quot;FB&quot;)<br />\nSPY是一款追蹤S&amp;P 500(標準普爾500指數)的ETF，每股股價相等於S&amp;P 500指數的10%，並且每個交易日均有極大成交量<br />\n<br />\nQ4. 用咩證劵行/銀行?<br />\nA4. 證劵行的話有富途、耀才等等，或者可以用IB或更平佣的8 securities等<br />\n銀行方面一般大銀行都可以，但手續費較高，詳情可自行google收費表<br />\n<br />\nQ5. 買賣美股有什麼注意事項?<br />\nA5. 美國政府會對任何於美國產生的收入徵稅，其中包括資產增值稅和股息稅<br />\n然而，海外投資者只會被收取30%股息稅，於股息派發時會預扣30%<br />\n另外，開設美股戶口前需要填寫W-8BEN表格以申報自己沒有美國戶籍，每一個美股投資戶口及每隔三年均需重新填寫一次<br />\n最後，由於美股以美元買賣，需要先將港元兌換美元才能買賣，匯兌時會有差價"},{"pid":"25ed5e423e530751d7574e2eccf54e6f0ce9acc7","tid":52442,"uid":49039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:36:51.000Z","msg":"點解買呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939100bd769b8cb7008f996f207a00e960ff52c7","tid":52442,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:42:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解買呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1. 指數型ETF風險較分散<br />\n2. S&amp;P 500指數除去兩次股災外歷年穩定上揚<br />\n3. 對美股認識唔夠深，不求跑贏大市，旦求同步於大市"},{"pid":"20373296aff5e33f24e034b7347e19c779f70e91","tid":52442,"uid":1747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:43:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解買呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買voo 斬得"},{"pid":"3924f2ebd32ab9b2571007887f00d5e90facd3a9","tid":52442,"uid":1747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:43:19.000Z","msg":"都*"},{"pid":"e33d525d14549df5e1e15c229e5c9eb61e3e3b51","tid":52442,"uid":7961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:49:01.000Z","msg":"股息稅是否可免？<br />\n手續會唔會好煩"},{"pid":"28d935c574ce818004fdd1d3ab0ae0af83e29c9e","tid":52442,"uid":1933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:49:46.000Z","msg":"每個月買一股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"d0aa703f77819a452f5acb835074f9aaee3d3618","tid":52442,"uid":34976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"其實買美股ETF重有好多選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSPY  = 標準普爾500指數<br />\nDIV  = 道瓊斯工業平均指數<br />\nQQQ = 納斯達克指數<br />\nIWM = 羅素2000指數 (小/中型公司指數，風險及回報較高)<br />\n<br />\n唔買SPY亦可以選VOO，類近於SPY並有較低管理費，但成交量遠少於SPY"},{"pid":"345c6742d8018c53955fead8e5decd27355fc259","tid":52442,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每個月買一股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n每月定股並非平均成本法(固定每個月投資固定金額)<br />\n因為我今個月先開始買，所以得一個記錄，而我今個月係買左4股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32255b3d0d8ebe98398f42d04c3fad70da386bf","tid":52442,"uid":8842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"最低幾錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2403dfc2a818ff7e8c32bedba931ab486aac24","tid":52442,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:55:46.000Z","msg":"有統計話，做short put spy 既risk adjusted  return係好過就咁Long spy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我覺得都係月供好d"},{"pid":"e387837c63d55b63cfb9c70a6faa61d449bb0895","tid":52442,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>股息稅是否可免？<br />\n手續會唔會好煩</blockquote><br />\ngoogle查到話可以退，但我岩岩開始未做過相關手續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d239dbe6598b139a83fa5551f56f51c5e147f1aa","tid":52442,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最低幾錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你指佣金?"},{"pid":"3ee3c67c9f2960bb75651aec506d2bc3c5a256a9","tid":52442,"uid":49039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:03:07.000Z","msg":"派息應該唔算多？"},{"pid":"bd669b4a7d65690bea4020bfe131e5cfb1d6cb98","tid":52442,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:08:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>派息應該唔算多？</blockquote><br />\nspy派息記錄<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nasdaq.com/zh/symbol/spy/dividend-history\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasdaq.com%2Fzh%2Fsymbol%2Fspy%2Fdividend-history&d=L8MSUQG7MI8HI5HnTx9053vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=0be2a993\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nasdaq.com/zh/symbol/spy/dividend-history</a>"},{"pid":"957ccaf586156bb0f873d10accafb4c0dcb63b92","tid":52442,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>派息應該唔算多？</blockquote><br />\nspy派息記錄<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nasdaq.com/zh/symbol/spy/dividend-history\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasdaq.com%2Fzh%2Fsymbol%2Fspy%2Fdividend-history&d=L8MSUQG7MI8HI5HnTx9053vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=0be2a993\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nasdaq.com/zh/symbol/spy/dividend-history</a></blockquote><br />\n依個網多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.moneydj.com/etf/x/Basic/Basic0005.xdjhtm?etfid=SPY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneydj.com%2Fetf%2Fx%2FBasic%2FBasic0005.xdjhtm%3Fetfid%3DSPY&d=L8MSUQG7MI8HI5HnTx9053vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=0c81e49f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.moneydj.com/etf/x/Basic/Basic0005.xdjhtm?etfid=SPY</a>"},{"pid":"6fbc80e3610c894e6e64d19c7647a7301dcb032b","tid":52442,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:18:14.000Z","msg":"SDY係標普既高息版本"},{"pid":"33cb85baddec6d4cd22fc08057c10ef96b7bbadb","tid":52442,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mwq50gtr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmwq50gtr&h=2130790f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月都開始玩月供brk.b<br />\n唔派息所以煩小樣野"},{"pid":"dfa241e7cdb3a7c05fb2189baa4e597e0200c297","tid":52442,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/mwq50gtr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmwq50gtr&h=2130790f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月都開始玩月供brk.b<br />\n唔派息所以煩小樣野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as