g src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你唔鐘意買太少令月續費相對較費，可以選擇季供<br />\n長期(5~10年以上)黎講相距唔遠"},{"pid":"92e696174f0d45b12a6019f1d2dede7466e43e20","tid":52442,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"手續費*"},{"pid":"c629d8c66fb05b9960794eb7e1c18662b06e7e89","tid":52442,"uid":1933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果我供<span style=\"color: red;\">2000HKD</span>，咪其實差唔多個個月都定股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n實際操作問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你唔鐘意買太少令月續費相對較費，可以選擇季供<br />\n長期(5~10年以上)黎講相距唔遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n牛牛好似都幾平，但我係驚一股價格太高，每月供款又唔多既話，好似做唔到月供個個平均成本效果（個股數變動唔大）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6996b243e5dfaa6e17e39258171aba4b8ad82f29","tid":52442,"uid":19925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8680210729450110c9c1041d544432cff1be95","tid":52442,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:45:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果我供<span style=\"color: red;\">2000HKD</span>，咪其實差唔多個個月都定股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n實際操作問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你唔鐘意買太少令月續費相對較費，可以選擇季供<br />\n長期(5~10年以上)黎講相距唔遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n牛牛好似都幾平，但我係驚一股價格太高，每月供款又唔多既話，好似做唔到月供個個平均成本效果（個股數變動唔大）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有乜所謂<br />\n根本所謂平均成本法只數字遊戲"},{"pid":"b7100409044c505090b3d93ce9165fb27ae88811","tid":52442,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T0