用8號仔咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa807729cd4aaf5e48e041618ca759bb4ab83eec","tid":52442,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無講到8號他幾好，得談笑。<br />\n美股其實可以退股息稅，只要股息唔超過某個金額，詳細我唔多記得，有興趣的巴打自己google下，台灣果邊都唔少教學。<br />\n<br />\n8號仔柒的地方係，佢唔會幫你記錄究竟自己預扣左你幾多股息，咁美股係一年派四次息，佢唔幫你計，即你要手動自己計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但其實是旦一間大規模小小的證券行，已經會有依d標準服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且有d證券行仲係有free commission ETF選擇，又係好適合月供，詳細又可以自己google下台灣果邊d文介紹返。<br />\n<br />\n總之，你有返小小資產（10萬美金左右），都會用IB la，就算無10萬美金，都唔會用8號仔咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇文好似話每年3500蚊免股息稅額，雖則唔知幾多年前數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7867c91d33db0fbfc44a78b05af09e11282c0056","tid":52442,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"有巴打可能話8號仔會計，<br />\n但我講清楚小小，<br />\n人地美國證券商果d係專登整一張統計表，寫到明金額係點，方便你一年報一次稅。<br />\n8號仔係會顯示扣左幾多，但佢唔會幫你做個一年統率表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823067a17567bd9be3c6a0baff279026cf8a7488","tid":52442,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無講到8號他幾好，得談笑。<br />\n美股其實可以退股息稅，只要股息唔超過某個金額，詳細我唔多記得，有興趣的巴打自己google下，台灣果邊都唔少教學。<br />\n<br />\n8號仔柒的地方係，佢唔會幫你記錄究竟自己預扣左你幾多股息，咁美股係一年派四次息，佢唔幫你計，即你要手動自己計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但其實是旦一間大規模小小的證券行，已經會有依d標準服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且有d證券行仲係有free commission ETF選擇，又係好適合月供，詳細又可以自己google下台灣果邊d文介紹返。<br />\n<br />\n總之，你有返小小資產（10萬美金左右），都會用IB la，就算無10萬美金，都唔會用8號仔咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇文好似話每年3500蚊免股息稅額，雖則唔知幾多年前數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以依家美股股息咁低，2%左右，3500美金，其實要17萬5000美金資產先有3500美金的股息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe8ac5a7b775e9aa6151795599de86994cfa2fa","tid":52442,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:17:36.000Z","msg":"另外，如果用TD-Ameritrade，有隻VTI，係Vanguard推出的美股指數ETF，其實同SpY差唔多，但commission free，vti指數係追蹤埋細價股，spy只係500強。<br />\n<br />\ncommission fee適合月供。"},{"pid":"1c13d21698beddd003a2a01a420c7fd8e93ab36b","tid":52442,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:21:07.000Z","msg":"除非你地用ib la，否則（應該）全部local 證券行/銀行都唔會幫你地整報稅表，咁你地就無得向美國政府claim返d股息稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果10萬美金以上，一定要用ib 囉，邊會仲用local野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79c5bdcaad49b4e8401819f592664766015e1e6","tid":52442,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:01:06.000Z","msg":"留名加正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209dd72e35cdd067f355e9863628ea7ce6897ee2","tid":52442,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>股息稅是否可免？<br />\n手續會唔會好煩</blockquote><br />\ngoogle查到話可以退，但我岩岩開始未做過相關手續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美帝要收30%冇走雞"},{"pid":"4f0df4fa1792385a5d900900b22c0c6623c73608","tid":52442,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:14:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除非你地用ib la，否則（應該）全部local 證券行/銀行都唔會幫你地整報稅表，咁你地就無得向美國政府claim返d股息稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果10萬美金以上，一定要用ib 囉，邊會仲用local野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過多五年等我真係有十萬美金我就會去開IB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f09e71423cab818b9a7341b237027cfa733042","tid":52442,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:42:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>股息稅是否可免？<br />\n手續會唔會好煩</blockquote><br />\ngoogle查到話可以退，但我岩岩開始未做過相關手續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美帝要收30%冇走雞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n更正原來有3500美金免稅額一年，先扣起錢，你再申請退稅。但問題係條例寫美國貿易及商業行為有關收入先屬於eci，買股票係個邊算唔算eci?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a0d3df016b0d595f12bcf4abbf7335b4b156d3","tid":52442,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:47:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>股息稅是否可免？<br />\n手續會唔會好煩</blockquote><br />\ngoogle查到話可以退，但我岩岩開始未做過相關手續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美帝要收30%冇走雞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n更正原來有3500美金免稅額一年，先扣起錢，你再申請退稅。但問題係條例寫美國貿易及商業行為有關收入先屬於eci，買股票係個邊算唔算eci?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係綱上又有一篇話唔得，美帝稅法真係好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">透過美國券商直接投資美股，所產生的股利到底能不能退稅？一直是台灣投資美國股市的朋友們所議論的話題。<br />\n<br />\n「過去」，我向來站在能的一方，因為真的有看人退成功過。<br />\n<br />\n但今年問題好像出現了，從三、四月報退稅至今，已超過半年，退稅仍沒下來。上去IRS查詢where is my tax return 我的退稅在哪兒?，發現還在審核中，這是相當不尋常的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n因為退稅都是跟前輩學的，自己從未認真研究過。昨天，上網去找一下，發現這段文字「No personal exemption or deductions can be applied against investment income (which is, technically, &quot;income not effectively connected with your US trade or business&quot;). Further, according to the IRS, &quot;if your sole U.S. business activity is trading securities through a U.S. resident broker or other agent, you are not engaged in a trade or business in the United States&quot; so the income is not effectively connected with a US trade or business.」網站：外國人能不能退稅<br />\n<br />\n這意思應該是：如果非居住於美國的外國人，在美國的商業行為，只有買賣股票，你的收入就不是ECI (Effectively Connected Income)，不符合個人免稅額的扣抵項目。也就是說：股利收入要扣30%的稅，且不能退。<br />\n<br />\n上IRS查詢，根據Publication 519規定IRS Publication 519，也有相似的句子如下：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然，退稅仍在審核中，看來30%的稅好像無法用個人免稅額的扣抵，這對我而言，影響不小。因為，如果每年若以成本計的股利為2.5%，光稅金就0.75%，相當高。在不違法的狀況下，我當然希望能退稅，如果不行，山不轉路轉，未來要將以追求股利成長的投資組合，做一些調整，還是會有好獲利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我不是稅務專家，以上只是個人的理解，做為自己的參考之用。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://funusstockmarket.blogspot.hk/2015/11/blog-post_22.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffunusstockmarket.blogspot.hk%2F2015%2F11%2Fblog-post_22.html&d=L8MSUQG7MI8HI5HnTx9053vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=31f76d7f\" target=\"_blank\">http://funusstockmarket.blogspot.hk/2015/11/blog-post_22.html</a>"},{"pid":"09b73abca4c5c285e7503aea648f02e1d668243a","tid":52442,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:04:07.000Z","msg":"問美國大使館會唔會有答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126ed76be9cd8e7686b6e6fa44ca051f2bb84e1e","tid":52442,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\ngoogle查到話可以退，但我岩岩開始未做過相關手續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美帝要收30%冇走雞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n更正原來有3500美金免稅額一年，先扣起錢，你再申請退稅。但問題係條例寫美國貿易及商業行為有關收入先屬於eci，買股票係個邊算唔算eci?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣好多例子已經成功退稅，google下吧"},{"pid":"53face09dc013599ea9634b7a5a7c7446a96718e","tid":52442,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:17:27.000Z","msg":"有兩部份，一部份係美國收入，另一部份係美國國外收入，國外收入肯定可以退稅，但美國